%N A398110 Number of 5-ary dyslexic mobiles with n internal nodes.
%H A398110 Andrew Howroyd, <a href="/A398110/b398110.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..500</a>
%H A398110 <a href="/index/Mo#mobiles">Index entries for sequences related to mobiles</a>
%F A398110 G.f. A(x) satisfies A(x) = 1 + x*(A(x)^5 + 4*A(x^5) + 5*A(x)*A(x^2)^2)/10.
%o A398110 (PARI) Vec(G(30,5)) \\ G(n,k) defined in A398109
%o A398110 (PARI) seq(n)={my(g=O(1)); for(i=0, n, g = 1+x*(g^5 + 4*subst(g,x,x^5) + 5*g*subst(g^2,x,x^2))/10); Vec(g)}
%Y A398110 Column k=5 of A398109.
